    Amber (Lith. gintaras), found on the Baltic Sea shores, was and is highly treasured and is the national gem of Lithuania. It is a fossil resin  which came from the sap of  several varieties of pines.
    Baltic amber is usually of a yellow, honey-like color, but may occur in many shades from pale yellow to dark brown. White pieces with a yellowish or bony tint are rare, and reddish, bluish and greenish tinted pieces are very rare. Some pieces of Baltic amber are transparent and clear, and others are cloudy and opaque.
    Pain relief is one of the main reasons people use Baltic amber. Though the resin itself isn't a painkiller, its succinic acid is believed to have analgesic properties that take the edge off of pain. Baltic amber has been used to alleviate all types of pain, from mild to severe. People have used Baltic amber to ease carpal tunnel syndrome, lessen back pain, alleviate menstrual cramps, ease arthritis, soothe migraine headaches, and help alleviate a baby's teething pains. Baltic amber may even restore energy, strengthen the immune system and promote general wellness. The salt of succinic acid may play an active role in cellular respiration and intercellular creation of energy.

Product name: Sea Turtle in Shell
Description:
We saw a nest {aka: clutch} of sea turtle eggs at the beach last night. They're protected by law so you can't touch them so I thought it would be fun to make crocheted baby turtles that kids can play with.
These cute baby sea turtles are great to decorate with or give as gifts. I make three options:

3) Unhatched Egg - This egg is crocheted as a whole egg and stuffed with polyfill. Buy one or several to show a turtle's nest. Sea turtles lay an average of 110 eggs in a clutch... you can pick how many you'd like in your collection.
**Please note: The "Unhatched Egg" option does not come with a baby turtle.**

Description:
Here is a fine German razor from the Krusius Brothers. Razor aficionados love blades made by these guys because of the wonderful steel's ability to hold an edge for a long time. This razor has been keeping its edge long before I was born and is still sharp. Meanwhile, I'm already losing my edge. 
 Ladies, competitive swimmers, and whoever else, don't rule this razor out for your legs and wherever else hair grows. It will give you the closest shave possible.
The blade has a straight cutting edge, and is free of chips, or cracks. There is minor surface staining on the steel, but I would not classify it as pitting. The only thing I did to clean this razor was hand rubbing with Simichrome polish. The scales (handle) are in wonderful unbroken condition. This razor appears to only need some light sharpening to be ready to mow your face, legs, or wherever hair removal is needed. If you plan on shaving with this check out http://straightrazorplace.com/ for everything you need to know about shaving with a razor like this.
The cutting edge is 2 7/8 inches long and the blade is 3/4 inches wide with a square (spike) point.

Product name: Stunning vintage men's 9ct gold Claddagh ring
Description:
A stunning vintage 9ct yellow gold men's Claddagh ring in excellent condition 
Fully hallmarked and professionally cleaned and polished this looks superb 
Written on the back of the band are the words .....
'With my two hands I give you my heart and crown it with my love'
Usage and symbolism
The Claddagh's distinctive design features two hands clasping a heart and usually surmounted by a crown. These elements symbolize the qualities of love (the heart), friendship (the hands), and loyalty (the crown). A "Fenian" Claddagh ring, without a crown, is a slightly different take on the design but has not achieved the level of popularity of the crowned version. Claddagh rings are relatively popular among the Irish and those of Irish heritage, such as Irish Americans, as cultural symbols and as friendship, engagement and wedding rings.

This rosary necklace is suitable for prayer, and contains gold beads which can be used to count along. Traditionally, rosary necklaces were used for veneration of Mary, and this necklace stays true to those roots. The necklace features an emblem of the Virgin Mother, along with a detailed crucifix on the end of the chain. 
Since the 16th century, rosary beads have been used for religious reasons. This modern handcrafted little rosary necklace allows you to connect with those traditions. It makes the perfect religious gift for women. 
Lovingly Handmade 
It is not very often that you can find a lovingly artisan crafted, handmade piece of jewelry at a reasonable price. At Pithuahua, we have an absolute dedication to quality, and take care to ensure every necklace that we send out to you is flawless in its unique beauty. 
This rosary necklace makes a great gift for women who prefer handmade jewelry, but who still want the charm, delight, and top quality. 
Measurements
This little rosary necklace weighs a nimble 5g.
It measures 11.75' from the top rosary bead to the bottom of the crucifix.
The circumference is 17' around the neck.
The necklace features a connector clasp for easy wearing and removing. 
Great Gift For Women 
This gold-filled little rosary necklace makes a perfect gift for women of all ages and walks of life. Whoever you buy this for will be delighted with the sight of this dainty necklace, with the quality of the materials and the craftsmanship, and with the thought of having something bought for them that they can't find anywhere else. 
The gift is especially significant for women who are religious or spiritual, especially Catholic women, and those who want to venerate Mary. Beautiful and functional, this little rosary necklace from Pithuahua is one of the best gifts you will find.
Etsy Best Seller 
We have had some really good feedback from this item, and it has become one of the most popular choices on Pithuahua, and a best seller on our Etsy store. Customers have given it 5* ratings across the board, and have been thrilled to leave us feedback about how much they have enjoyed their necklace. 
If there was ever proof that a gift is worth giving, it is in the positive reviews received from those who have already enjoyed the rosary necklace. 
Practical Information
We ship worldwide from the United States, and make sure that our shipping is as prompt as possible. We won't leave you waiting longer than you have to. The rosary necklace comes gift wrapped as standard, ideal for if you are making the purchase to reward someone else. 
Contact us if you have any questions, or feel free to make an order to get your gold-filled little rosary necklace sent to you now.

Product name: Custom Back to the future 2 Air Mag illumination Boot Strap EL Panels.
Description:
Kit consists of: 2 x Custom made 24mm x 44mm EL panels with Nike Logo Imprinted directly onto the EL Panel.
These panels are to be used as a conversion for the Nike Air Mag V2 replica boot.
This conversion will require some crafting skill as the original boot strap will need to be parted using a Hairdryer or Heat Gun and the original Nike panel cut out using a Craft knife so the EL panel can be glued in its place.
There is a good tutorial on You Tube about Nike Air Mag V2 Conversions, search JediFyfe, he specialises in such conversions.
We supply the EL panels only, the power source for the EL panels can be wired from the Lithium battery in the sole of the Nike Air Mag V2 as described by JediFyfe on You tube or powered externally by plugging in a micro power pack such as a CR2032 Coin Cell Inverter.
Any questions about crafting the conversion or selecting power source please email me and i will help you out, i have done this conversion a few times so am pretty good at it.
